<h2>Digital Foundations: Course Content</h2>
<ul>
  <li><b>Social Media Basics & Personal Branding:</b> Learn how to set up and optimize your social media profiles for professional growth and networking.</li>
  <li><b>Communication Skills for Online Work:</b> Master the art of clear, effective communication for remote jobs and freelancing.</li>
  <li><b>Mindset & Goal Setting:</b> Develop a growth mindset and learn practical goal-setting techniques to stay motivated.</li>
  <li><b>Introduction to Online Earning Methods:</b> Explore various ways to earn money online, from freelancing to affiliate marketing.</li>
  <li><b>How Referral Networks Work:</b> Understand the basics of referral marketing and how to build your own network.</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<p><b>Tips for Success:</b> Complete all lessons, take notes, and join the community group for support and networking.</p>